children.text: Use the Application Environment Configuration wizard to initially define the Agent Groups/tiers and Agent mappings required to configure your application processes and web servers to load the Agent and connect to the AppMon Collector. During the wizard set up, you are prompted to download the Agent installer appropriate for your environment and configure the Agent connection string.
